      "id": "PopularPost102466",
      "post_content": "The thing people neglect about eidolons is that every single one of them works without you even having to play it. All you do is have a deck stuffed with multicolour which discards them for benefit. For example any card which allows you to draw one, discard one like a looter, or lore broker, anything like that, you will essentially end up drawing cards for free.\n  \n   \nI have a deck which runs 8 of them and never plays them. Just uses them for free discard.",
      "posted_by": "Baconradar",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost102466\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">The thing people neglect about eidolons is that every single one of them works without you even having to play it. All you do is have a deck stuffed with multicolour which discards them for benefit. For example any card which allows you to draw one, discard one like a looter, or lore broker, anything like that, you will essentially end up drawing cards for free.\r<br/> <br/>I have a deck which runs 8 of them and never plays them. Just uses them for free discard.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '102466'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy42535\">Baconradar</span>\r\n                                (9/16/2010 3:49:12 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../I